HEADWORD: Specialist
<hw>Spe"cial*ist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who devotes
himself to some specialty; <as>as, a medical <ex>specialist</ex>, one
who devotes himself to diseases of particular parts of the body, as the
eye, the ear, the nerves, etc.</as></def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Speciality</ent>⟦br⟧
